This is my personal project that will slowly coalesce into my dissertation.
I am a graduate student, my academic profile is here:
http://www.css.gmu.edu/?q=node/127

This particular project involves setting a simple, general purpose agent based economic model somehow reminiscent of "Business Dynamics" by Steedman.
The basic approach of it I describe here:
https://dl.dropbox.com/u/9133731/zeroKnowledge.pdf

I am going to present that paper and preliminary results at the Eastern Economic Association Meeting in the coming (2013) May.